block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: The Cutter designed by Paul Jackson is a really fast origami paper airplane. The extra mass at the front of the paper airplane allows it to zoom forward as though it has a turbo booster. This fast origami paper airplane is also the 43 member of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane challenge. Enjoy! If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 42 : Star Clipper by Andrew Dewar", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/B1dOrqIqzkQ Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
